topIssues.title: Conductor: Allow flashblocks port auto-assignment
topIssues.author: axelKingsley
topIssues.body:
In the triage of `TestControlLoop/TestFlashblocksHandlerIntegration`, I found the likely culprit was the way in which the port was being bound:
- Test gets a random port
- Test releases the port
- (In the meantime, other things are likely to be assigned the port)
- Test spins up the conductor with the port
- Port in use, test fails


In attempting to fix this, I discovered that there is *no way* to enable port auto-assignment for `WebsocketServerPort`:

https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/25032f2e17e8d0c085697a4ad75e13f3787ad535/op-conductor/conductor/service.go#L326-L333

**Steps to Reproduce**

$ docker run --rm \

topPRs.title: all: Update op-geth to use blobGasUsed field for DA footprint
topPRs.author: sebastianst
topPRs.body:
**Description**

Follow up to https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/pull/17466 to update op-geth to https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/op-geth/pull/694, finally using the `blobGasUsed` field for the DA footprint, instead of sharing the `gasUsed` field like in the previous design.

**Tests**

Fixed and extended existing acceptance test to cover configurability and explicitly assert correct base fee update calculation.

Also improved some devstack DSL functions to offer more generic `WaitFor...` methods.

Action tests are added in a follow up.

**Metadata**

Fixes https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/op-geth/issues/691

topPRs.title: op-fetcher: Support the CANNON_KONA FaultDisputeGame
topPRs.author: Inphi
topPRs.body:
Add the `CANNON_KONA` game implementation address to op-fetcher.

`CANNON_KONA` is currently introduced to chains as a "DevFeature". It needs to be enabled when deploying or upgrading existing chains before the new game implementation is set.
To ensure that op-fetcher is backwards compatible with chains that don't have the `DevFeature` enabled, op-fetcher displays the new game type only if it detects that it's enabled. 

fixes https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/issues/17740
